[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":207},["Reactive",2],{"IV7crRtdlG":3,"HORZY6Opx5":33,"aXVWNnQrRF":58,"gYbd58LvKq":123,"6TzEvRXQAp":148,"6sWAIcTsx6":200,"_apollo:default":206},{"articles":4,"tags":32},[5],{"id":6,"title":7,"summary":8,"cover_image":9,"body":17,"tags":18,"__typename":31},"a1a783bc-7f41-4df1-8284-14b7969a0199","在 MeeGo 使用快倉六","本文講述如何在 MeeGo 1.0 for Netbooks 安裝及使用快速倉頡第六代中文輸入法。",{"id":10,"folder":11,"filename_disk":12,"filename_download":13,"type":14,"description":11,"filesize":15,"__typename":16},"a88d0d1c-9f56-4e1f-a1b5-de000c44baaf",null,"a88d0d1c-9f56-4e1f-a1b5-de000c44baaf.png","MeeGo-Screenshot-1.png","image/png","62490","directus_files","\u003Cp>本文講述如何在 MeeGo 1.0 for Netbooks 安裝及使用快速倉頡第六代中文輸入法。\u003Cbr>\u003Ca href=\"/content/在-meego-10-使用快倉六\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://cms.scj2000.net/assets/113f596d-c62c-401b-8d8a-80bae934bb86?width=592&amp;height=370\" alt=\"MeeGo Scj6\">\u003C/a>\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>\u003C/p>\n\u003C!--break-->\n\u003Cp>用戶須先選用中文的 MeeGo 語言設定，並選用 scim 作為預設輸入法平台。\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>開啟終端機程式，以 su - 轉換為 root 身份從 lazyfai 之 scim-tables 及本站之 scj2000 之軟件庫下載及執行安裝。\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp style=\"font-family: courier;\">su -\u003Cbr>yum install wget\u003Cbr>cd /etc/yum.repos.d/\u003Cbr>wget http://lazyfai.fedorapeople.org/MeeGo/meego-lazyfai.repo\u003Cbr>wget http://yum.scj2000.net/scj2000.repo\u003Cbr>yum install scim-tables-chinese-extra\u003Cbr>yum install scim-tables-zh-scj\u003Cbr>exit\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>嗚謝 \u003Ca href=\"http://lazyfai.fedorapeople.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">lazyfai\u003C/a> 為 MeeGo 的 scim-tables 及相關軟件建立軟件庫。 \u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>安裝完成後請重新開機。\u003Cbr>在文字輸入方塊可以按 [Ctrl]+[空格] 鍵開始輸入中文。(已知部份 MeeGo 軟未能調用中文輸入法。)\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>\u003Ca title=\"Screenshot #1\" href=\"/sites/default/files/MeeGo-Screenshot-1.png\" rel=\"lightbox\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://cms.scj2000.net/assets/a88d0d1c-9f56-4e1f-a1b5-de000c44baaf?width=800&amp;height=480\" alt=\"MeeGo Screenshot 1\">\u003C/a>\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>\u003Ca title=\"Screenshot #2\" h